{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"baf5b0d6c3","title":"在北京卫戍区关于部队战备野营拉练总结报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"74beaaf6df","index":0,"year":1970,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"baf5b0d6c3"}],"tags":[{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"952d481289","type":"title","text":"在北京卫戍区关于部队战备野营拉练总结报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"baf5b0d6c3"},{"id":"70c7db1298","type":"paragraph","text":"在北京卫戍区关于部队战备野营拉练总结报告上的批语","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"baf5b0d6c3"},{"id":"68c1998d04","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"baf5b0d6c3"},{"id":"486604c813","type":"paragraph","text":"1970.11.24","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"baf5b0d6c3"},{"id":"157eea0912","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"baf5b0d6c3"},{"id":"345d488723","type":"paragraph","text":"此件可阅，我看很好。请你和黄永胜同志商量一下，全军是否利用冬季实行长途野营训练一次，每个军可分两批（或不分批），每批两个月，实行官兵团结、军民团结。三支、两军者不在内。但大、中、小学（高年级）学生是否利用寒假也可以实行野营训练一个月。工厂是否可以抽少数工人（例如四分之一，但生产不能减少）进行野营练习。请与中央各同志一商。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"baf5b0d6c3"},{"id":"413dff09a4","type":"paragraph","text":"如不这样训练，就会变成老爷兵。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"baf5b0d6c3"}],"page":{"id":"0bacfcddb1","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"baf5b0d6c3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}